ActNational Capital Act
SubjectOrder Approving that the NCC Extend the Lease with Marc G. Sauvé Professional Corporation
PrecisOrder approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION grant one option to extend the lease with MARC G. SAUVÉ PROFESSIONAL CORPORATION, for a period of five years, beginning on December 1, 2028, for the real property located at 283 Sussex Drive, in Ottawa, Ontario.
